---
title: Mediterranean-Inspired Lamb Burgers with Sweet Potatoes
description: The noble burger, a thing of such delicious, dribble-down-your-chin simplicity, can be re-invented time and time again to create the most divine dinnertime results. For this incarnation, we've put a Greek twist on it with ground lamb and feta cheese!
